<a name="menu"></a>
<h2>Municipal and State flags for the United States Menu</h2>

<p><i>Editor's note:</i> The names of the pages for the states and the district of the United States are composed as <code>us-xx.html</code>,  in which <code>xx</code> is the postal code of the state or the district.  The images are named <code>us-xx.gif</code> in the same way.</p>  

